{"tid":907824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★賀！東涌成大媽舞林聖地　勁歌響徹天","createTime":"2018-11-19T06:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T10:55:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":274,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"591ec488a1dea8f39858cb730eef6d7f031bcbfb","tid":907824,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181119/photo/bkn-20181119130023863-1119_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181119140918\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181119%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181119130023863-1119_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181119140918&h=5e6b14db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或許不少大媽的夢想是要成為舞蹈家，這團火不管在何地，都忍不住要「爆」了。這股熱情最近燒到去東涌，有兩名大媽在東薈城外勁歌熱舞，十分陶醉。<br />\n<br />\n片段於星期日（18日）被上載至Facebook群組「PLAY HARD 玩硬」，在東涌東薈城近港鐵站出口的空地中，有一名身穿紅色連身裙和紅色高跟鞋的大媽與另一名身穿碎花裙的大媽翩翩起舞。<br />\n<br />\n二人配合流暢，隨着節奏強勁的音樂不斷旋轉和跳躍。當時周遭坐滿休息的旅客，細心地欣賞着這「餘興節目」。拍攝者無奈表示︰「佢跳得好enjoy（享受）添喎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181119/bkn-20181119130023863-1119_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181119%2Fbkn-20181119130023863-1119_00822_001.html&d=1qQUYiz6aatzlv%2BlB%2BK4%2FpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e31287e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181119/bkn-20181119130023863-1119_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e338bd92fda6cadce95f73ed0715abf1e8f768d3","tid":907824,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59db981b87fb914de4eef2601999d372eaf50e4","tid":907824,"uid":14739,"like":127,"dislike":3,"score":124,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:30:31.000Z","msg":"青衣準備"},{"pid":"0e4cff560c8ef7cfae596dd2524c20b1fd569cfd","tid":907824,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"抵啦<im